org.jetel.graph.analyse

Interface InspectedComponent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInspectedComponent, BasicInspectedComponent

    public interface InspectedComponent
    This interface is used by GraphCycleInspector for graph layout tracking. This is handler for a component and provides iterable view to all connected components.
    See Also:
    GraphCycleInspector, SingleGraphProvider
